<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śakābdaṁbulu 1055 gu nēṇḍu śrīmadanaṁttava
<lb n="2" break="no"/>rmmadēvara pravarddhamānavijayarājyasaṁvatsa 59
<lb n="3"/>śrāhikuṁbhamānamuna sūryyagrahaṇa nimi
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ttamuna nakarāna śrīmadhukīśvaradēvaraku māli ya
<lb n="5" break="no"/>nāyaka demāṇḍināyakuni koḍuku rācapaḍihasta pu
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ravari sūrapōtu peṭṭina Akhaṇḍavarttidīpa 1 ki mā 5 ṇṭiki
<lb n="7"/>varāhavaṁttaniya paṁpuna lōkayavairiya Uttaramu
<lb n="8" break="no"/>na baṁdda tūrppuna jēlalōvugā nāluvu <unclear>mū</unclear>la<unclear>la</unclear>
<lb n="9"/>rālu 7 veṭṭina bhūmi <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> ruvuriki reṁḍu jēnakōlaṁ golacipeṭṭi
<lb n="10" break="no"/>na puṭlu reṁ <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> tūmulu vadi nni dininācaṁdrārkka
<lb n="11"/>mu naḍapiṁppaṁgalavāru nakaravuvāḍa nāyaku lu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
